      "amount": "1 teaspoon",
      "notes": "ground"
    },
    {
      "name": "banana leaves",
      "amount": "4 large",
      "notes": "fresh"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a large pan, heat the lardons-render over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion to the pan and cook until softened.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger to the pan and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the cumin and coriander to the pan and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the blueberries to the pan and cook until they start to release their juice.",
    "Spoon the blueberry mixture onto the center of each banana leaf.",
    "Fold the banana leaves over the filling to form a packet and bake for 20 minutes."
  ],
